<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Security Checklist</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f1f3f6;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    ul.checklist {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    ul.checklist li {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    ul.checklist li::before {
      content: "‚úÖ";
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: green;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    ul.checklist li.warning::before {
      content: "üõ°Ô∏è";
      color: red;
    }

    .header-icon {
      font-size: 28px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    h2 span {
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <div class="container">
    <h2><span class="header-icon">üîí</span><span>Security Checklist</span></h2>
    <ul class="checklist">
      <li>Inputs are sanitized and validated</li>
      <li>Passwords are hashed using bcrypt</li>
      <li>Login uses secure logic and bcrypt.compare</li>
      <li>No XSS or direct injection via user input</li>
      <li>Winston logging is enabled</li>
      <li>Directory structure organized and safe</li>
      <li>Nmap scan tested and documented</li>
      <li>Static files properly served</li>
      <li class="warning">HTTPS recommended for deployment</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
